      • getIlfo

        public int getIlfo()
        Returns the ilfo, an index to the document's hpllfo, which describes the automatic number formatting of the paragraph. A value of zero means it isn't numbered.(返回ilfo，文档的hpllfo的索引，它描述段落的自动数字格式。值为零意味着它没有编号。)

      • getIlvl

        public int getIlvl()
        Returns the multi-level indent for the paragraph. Will be zero for non-list paragraphs, and the first level of any list. Subsequent levels in hold values 1-8.(返回段落的多层收件箱。对于非列表段落，并且是任何列表的第一级，将为零。后续水平保持值为1-8。)

      • getLvl

        public int getLvl()
        Returns the heading level (1-8), or 9 if the paragraph isn't in a heading style.(返回标题级别（1-8），如果段落不采用标题样式，则返回9。)

      • getTabStopsNumber

        public int getTabStopsNumber()
        Returns number of tabs stops defined for paragraph. Must be >= 0 and <= 64.(返回为段落定义的制表符数量。必须>= 0且<= 64。)
        Returns:
        number of tabs stops defined for paragraph. Must be >= 0 and <= 64(为段落定义的制表符数量。必须>= 0且<= 64)

      • getTabStopsPositions

        public int[] getTabStopsPositions()
        Returns array of positions of itbdMac tab stops(返回itbdMac制表位的位置数组)
        Returns:
        array of positions of itbdMac tab stops(itbdMac选项卡停止位置数组)
